{"tid":1882271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城攻略］不推文回覆對抗PR攻勢","createTime":"2020-02-16T06:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T06:58:14.000Z","uid":260296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30fe9c26dcd5b163e7343504372265fffcffa06d","tid":1882271,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"有句話叫做「抗爭都要抖氣」<br />\n本p牌狗係十分認同，報仇放負同玩下膠po係有可能共享，之不過係要拎到個平衡<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有鑑於pr公司五毛現正係連登發動攻勢</span></span>，不斷利用群眾心理學或者自己友圍內推post嘅手段，想推散大家軍心<br />\n<br />\n想贏嘅手足，有個好重要嘅元素想介紹番：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">習慣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">習慣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同<span style=\"color: gold;\">習慣</span><br />\n<br />\n襯依家主力放文宣戰嘅時間，養成習慣，所有手足係出po之前，自己諗下個po有冇上熱門嘅戰略意義，無的話：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係標題或者內文標明「善用不推文」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一來方便順手提醒大家，二來幫手傳播集中抗爭嘅意念<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"085380ef97b2692f052fd1d8e8016acda5afc71c","tid":1882271,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=d5915d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"fe35cda0b82ab8b56dea2632ef94ad9e63ebcb2e","tid":1882271,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"新晉黃色Youtuber 你訂閱咗未啊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.